               <p>JOHN CHIDLEY. I am a <rs id="t18310908-128-viclabel697" type="occupation">bookseller</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-128-victim1060 t18310908-128-viclabel697"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18310908-128-crimeloc698">Goswell-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-128-crimeloc698" type="placeName" value="Goswell-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-128-crimeloc698" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-128-off695 t18310908-128-crimeloc698"></join>. On the 20th of July the prisoner came and bought a book for 3d. - he left hastily, and in consequence of information I went after him; he was running fast - I stopped him, and took him back; he produced these books, which are mine.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I travel with books for sale; I laid my bundle on the counter, and these books were tied in my bundle with others, by mistake.</p>
